<https://haulaah.github.io/CIRPO/incident/32848> a :Incident ;
    :hasIncidentId "32848" ;
    :hasIncidentName "Ransomware Attack" ;
    :hasIncidentDescription "A ransomware attack was detected across the IROrg network after multiple endpoints executed suspicious binaries, initiated encoded PowerShell activity, and connected to malicious external infrastructure. Shortly afterward, the file server srv‑web01 began encrypting data using the .df_locked extension, accompanied by ransom notes in affected directories. Initial compromise originated from user workstations and progressed via credential misuse, leading to lateral movement and deployment of the ransomware payload. This case tracks the investigation, containment, and recovery actions following the incident." ;
    :hasIncidentSeverity "2" ;
    :hasIncidentCreationDateTime "2026-02-24T14:42"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    :hasConfirmationDateTime "2026-02-24T14:41"^^xsd:dateTime ;
